Library of MTK camera utilities.

This library is pre-built by MediaTek internal.


WHAT IT DOES?
=============
This static library provides utilities such as creating JPEG buffer and making Exif header.
It is required from many different camrera features.

HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================
It needs the following library from AOSP:
1.  liblog.so
2.  libcutils.so

and the following libs from MediaTek:
1.  libm4u.so
2.  libmpo.so
3.  libcamera_client_mtk.so

All source/dependency modules of this module are already put in
'vendor/mediatek/libs' folder.

HOW TO USE IT?
==============

Provide api for camera HAL to control the camera features.
all api interface are at (vendor/mediatek/proprietary/hardware/mtkcam)

All the source code of this library were written by MediaTek co..
